headline: First of Its Kind HPV Self-Collection Study Launched to Improve Cervical Cancer Screening in Underserved Communities
summary: A first of its kind Human Papillomavirus (HPV) self-collection screening pilot program aimed at improving cervical cancer screening in underserved communities has officially launched in Texas. HPV is the cause of virtually all cervical cancers.
